ZH: 我在林中发现了一支步枪。
EN: I found a rifle in the woods.

ZH: 这家军事博物馆展示了各种款式的步枪。
EN: This military museum displays various types of rifles.

ZH: 他手里紧紧握着一把步枪。
EN: He tightly grasped a rifle in his hand.

ZH: 这支步枪可以射击很远的距离。
EN: This rifle can shoot at a long distance.

ZH: 军队正在对新型步枪进行试射。
EN: The army is conducting test shooting of the new rifle.

ZH: 这支步枪非常精确，命中率很高。
EN: This rifle is very accurate and has a high hit rate.

ZH: 这款步枪的设计非常现代化。
EN: The design of this rifle is very modern.

ZH: 他将步枪放在肩膀上，准备好射击。
EN: He put the rifle on his shoulder, ready to shoot.

ZH: 这支步枪有一个可伸缩的枪托。
EN: This rifle has a collapsible buttstock.

ZH: 他在步枪上装上了一个光学瞄准镜。
EN: He attached an optical scope to the rifle.

ZH: 这支步枪采用了先进的射击系统。
EN: This rifle adopts an advanced shooting system.

ZH: 这支步枪的射速非常快。
EN: This rifle has a very high firing rate.

ZH: 战士们受训时要学会如何使用步枪。
EN: Soldiers need to learn how to use rifles during training.

ZH: 这支步枪重量适中，很容易携带。
EN: This rifle has a moderate weight and is easy to carry.

ZH: 他得到了一支步枪的许可证。
EN: He obtained a license for a rifle.

ZH: 我曾经使用过步枪进行射击训练。
EN: I have used rifles for shooting training before.

ZH: 这种步枪的枪管很长，非常适合远程射击。
EN: The barrel of this rifle is long, making it ideal for long-range shooting.

ZH: 他将步枪调整到最佳射击位置。
EN: He adjusted the rifle to its optimal shooting position.

ZH: 这支步枪是他在军队服役期间获得的。
EN: He obtained this rifle during his military service.

ZH: 这支步枪使用了新的材料和技术。
EN: This rifle uses new materials and technology.
